item.title: Need help urgently!
item.dc:creator: @Scully Scully
item.description:
@Scully wrote:

Okay here’s what you do.

  1. Download the 508 cache.
  2. Put that cache in your C: drive in a folder named cache508.
  3. Run the server.
  4. Rune the client.

That should do it.

Off topic: The need help urgently thing doesn’t get you help faster it just usually makes you seem annoying and such. Post with the name of your problem and look your post over for spelling errors and grammar mistakes before posting. Doing this will make it easier to understand for the reader and yourself at a later date.
